captions.text:
"Rosie, want to go to the movies?" How
'bout this... "Rosie. Movies, let's go!"

"Rosie. You look like someone who loves
the cinema!" Or maybe... "Rosie! -"

You did not! Uh-huh, yeah! One minute.
Hello, Timothy.

Go on in, Max is home. I'm
back, go on... You did not!!
Hey, Timmy!
Hi, Max.

Max, let me ask you a question... See, I know this
certain dude... And he likes this particular girl...

And the girl doesn't even notice he's alive most
of the time... What should my friend be doing?

Tim... Does this friend of
yours wear a baseball cap?
Well... usually.

And by any chance would his name be Tim?
Here's what you

should tell your friend. Girls
like dangerous guys who

aren't really dangerous. That's
why they love rap stars.

SO BARK SOME STYLIN' RAP /
CATCH ROSIE IN YOUR TRAP / Yo!

Oh, is that right? Then what? How sweet!
Then he said that?

THINK YOU KNOW ME, YO? / THERE'S A ME
YOU DON'T KNOW / A TALL DARK STRANGER

/ WITH A TASTE FOR DANGER / I'M SO
DARN COOL / THE GIRLS ALL DROOL...
Yeah, I'm still here, I'm listening...
Yeah!
I can't believe it!

I'M FIT, I'M FLY, I'M PHAT, I'M FINE
/ WANNA DATE ME? THEN GET IN LINE! /

SITTIN' BY YOU IS A DREAM COME TRUE /
IT'S YOUR MOVE, GIRL. WHATYA GONNA DO?

Could you please be quieter? It's really
hard to talk on the phone in this house...
Yo! Sorry.

Okay... so rap's not her thing... Don't worry
about it, buddy... It's not a problem.

This is our chance. We can
find out what she does like!
Success! Oh, man, it's perfect!

Hey, Max! I'm guessing this person's
here to see you! This one's

even wierder than your other friends.
Uh-huh, I'm back... That's cool...
BABY!

GIRL, YOU NEVER FAIL / NOSIREE
/ TO MAKE ME WAG MY TAIL / YOU

SEE / IT'S TWITCHING LIKE A
HUMMINGBIRD / SO FAST IT'S BLURRED...

I guess that didn't really work either, did it?
If I were Rosie,

I'd already have given in.
What are you going to do next?
I don't know.

I had a thought! She really,
really loves to watch Mexican

movies. Like, a lot! Maybe she'd
like you if you were Mexican.

OH, SENORITA! / HOW YOU MAKE MY HEART BEAT-A /
BOOM BOOM SHAKA TAKA / BOOM BOOM SHAKA TAKA

Fantastic, man! Fantastic! This one is
going to work!

And he's like what? No way!
Uh-huh. You are insane!

I don't really like any particuar type at all.
But I hate it when they

pretend to be something that they're not!
I like when boy is just himself...

Just himself...just himself...just
himself...just himself
Good riddance, "boom boom shaka taka" ...
Oh, hey, Tim!
Hey, Rosie. You want to go to the movies?
I'd love to!
